      "replayEndSec": 15.126152,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-02.fc135b6e.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.042449,
      "textHash": "fc135b6ed9c522d336e24ffb3bc5606ce60e036792956bdab8858a726239d793",
      "narrationText": "Nüüd konteinerid. See vaade loetleb kõik töötavad konteinerid kõigis masina repositooriumides -- nimi, olek, tervis, CPU, mälu, lisaks sellele, millisele repositooriumile igaüks kuulub.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-02-after.a56bb4c5.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.787755,
      "afterTextHash": "a56bb4c5bd73e61263f27aa3efaaa2cc133966d0251581760589afc7238b4207"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-monitoring-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 15.126152,
      "replayEndSec": 24.385141,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-03.def5e9f5.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.717551,
      "textHash": "def5e9f5b23e62344d7e69259899fd4fc407243da9de783e5f02fed9b3b63611",
      "narrationText": "Ja repositooriumid ise. Suurus, ühendamise olek, Dockeri deemoni olek, kettakasutus. Kõik, mida pead teadma iga isoleeritud keskkonna kohta masinas.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-03-after.495fc923.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.866122,
      "afterTextHash": "495fc9236361795074beeb04ff0991efe3b7e385b53187e6f7dfc1bcb7625c1a"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-monitoring-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 24.385141,
      "replayEndSec": 32.334422,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-04.952a05b4.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.672653,
      "textHash": "952a05b4536e2ed98fa434c4bc86a30d8f56990967826944609b708635adf8ba",
      "narrationText": "CLI machine query annab sulle kõik korraga. Süsteemiteave, konteinerid, repositooriumid, kõik koos. Käivita korra ja sul on täielik pilt.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-04-after.f98de3e9.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.690612,
      "afterTextHash": "f98de3e93233ea29ee2af4c032c5ac70274ba207dab7258d00d79c0b4d83a92c"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-monitoring-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 32.334422,
      "replayEndSec": 38.502093,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-05.ac6cfcac.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.229388,
      "textHash": "ac6cfcace593e6a47aa0c353d7a2f1c11883a8e2aa235c5e162eca03a7513af5",
      "narrationText": "Ja lõpuks CLI doctor kohaliku tervise kontrolliks sülearvutis. Node, SSH võti, renet, Docker -- kõik asjad, millest CLI ise sõltub. See on terve sari. Paigaldamisest monitoorimiseni, kõik sinu terminalist.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-monitoring/tutorial-monitoring-05-after.516ff012.mp3",
